<BaseLayout
  title="Th√© au Jardin"
  description="A haven of greenery and natural space in the heart of Brussels - workshops, activities and community for GOLDIES 65+"
  lang="en"
  currentPath="the-au-jardin"
>
  <div class="page-header with-hero hero-the-au-jardin">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Th√© au Jardin</h1>
      <p>Your Garden. Your Community. Your Sanctuary.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="content-section">
    <div class="intro-section">
      <p class="lead">
        WARNED presents Th√© au Jardin: a haven of greenery and a natural space in the heart of the city. Nestled at Kauwberg, in the beautiful commune of Uccle, our house and accompanying gardens constitute a safe gathering "freespace" where you are encouraged to learn, connect, grow and share on a social, emotional, mental and physical level.
      </p>
      <p class="lead">
        We openly embrace our differences: those who wish to be active, those who are extroverts, those who live alone, or those who prefer a slower pace are all welcome. Th√© au Jardin is an inclusive project in which the links between younger and older generations is forged and circularity is key: we collaborate in harmony, everything we need comes from and feeds back into the community.
      </p>
      <p class="goal"><strong>The principle is simple:</strong> just come as you are and grow with us.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>What To Expect</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-2">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>üå≥ Lush Gardens</h3>
        <p>Take a moment, sit back, close your eyes and enjoy the tranquility of the marvellous gardens.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>‚òï Tea & Coffee</h3>
        <p>Stay hydrated with our special teas and coffee.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>üç∞ Snacks</h3>
        <p>Cake and other tea time treats await you!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>üßò Movement</h3>
        <p>Move your body during dance, yoga, tai chi and other physical activity workshops.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>üí¨ Conversation</h3>
        <p>Catch up, gossip and make new friends.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>üé™ Entertainment</h3>
        <p>Have fun with your fellow GOLDIES!</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Our Current Programme of Workshops & Activities</h2>

    <div class="programme-card">
      <h3>üåø 'Garden of Movement' - Wednesday</h3>
      <div class="programme-details">
        <ul>
          <li>Tai Chi Session</li>
          <li>Walking, sports and movement classes specially designed for the GOLDIE body</li>
          <li>Focus on sustainable approach to health: rediscovering our connection to nature, water, the soil and the forest</li>
          <li>Learn through movement how to adopt a more ethical and less predatory way of life</li>
          <li>Designed to emancipate the body and mind, inspired by human permaculture</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="info-box">
          <p><strong>Location:</strong> The Garden - 22 Kauwberg, 1180 Uccle</p>
          <p><strong>Schedule:</strong> All year long. Garden is open 1-5pm. Workshops start at a fixed time but you can come and go whenever you please. "Chant√¢ge" starts at 3.30pm under the direction of Oceane, our choir director.</p>
          <p><strong>Refreshments:</strong> Unlimited tea & coffee</p>
          <p><strong>Fee:</strong> Voluntary contribution</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="programme-card">
      <h3>‚ú® 'Garden of the Senses' - Thursday</h3>
      <div class="programme-details">
        <ul>
          <li>Chair Dance Workshop</li>
          <li>Your wellbeing takes centre stage</li>
          <li>Designed by invited guest instructors</li>
          <li>Tailor-made combination of GOLDIE friendly activities to awaken your senses, explore your emotions and enliven your sensuality</li>
