        </ul>
        <div class="info-box">
          <p><strong>Location:</strong> The Garden - 22 Kauwberg, 1180 Uccle</p>
          <p><strong>Schedule:</strong> Thursdays from 1-5pm</p>
          <p><strong>Refreshments:</strong> Unlimited tea & coffee</p>
          <p><strong>Fee:</strong> Voluntary contribution</p>
        </div>
